      "issue": "Multiple duplicate headings",
      "detail": "'Highlights from the last quarter' appears three times as an H2, and 'A Journey of Resilience and Hope: Farhan's Success Story' and 'Vision-Aid's collaboration with Christian Medical College (CMC), Vellore' each appear twice. This makes it impossible for assistive technology users to distinguish between these sections."
    },
    {
      "issue": "Flat, non-hierarchical structure for content that should be grouped",
      "detail": "The page presents a long flat list of H2 headings (success stories, news items, quarterly highlights) without any grouping or parent sections. These items logically belong under categories (e.g., 'Success Stories', 'News & Events', 'Quarterly Updates') but are all siblings at the same level, making the outline overwhelming and hard to navigate."
    },
    {
      "issue": "Heading 'For more details click here' is vague and non-descriptive",
      "detail": "This H2 heading describes an action rather than the content of the section. It provides no meaningful information about what the section contains."
    },
    {
      "issue": "Heading used for a call-to-action / instructional text rather than a section label",
      "detail": "'Any gift of Smart Assistive Technology will be doubled by a generous matching grant.' and 'Note:- Email is the preferred and recommended way to contact us.' are full sentences used as headings. They function as body content or notes, not as section labels."
    },
